n\u002Fworld_war_1\u002Fcasualties\u002F\"\u003ECommonwealth War Graves Commission\u003C\u002Fa\u003E. World War I is among the deadliest wars in modern history."}},{"is":"paragraph","props":{"text":"\u003Ca href=\"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.foxnews.com\u002Fscience\u002Fsoldiers-faith-rare-bible-carried-at-the-battle-of-bunker-hill-has-moving-inscriptions\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ESOLDIER&apos;S FAITH: RARE BIBLE CARRIED AT THE BATTLE OF BUNKER HILL HAS MOVING INSCRIPTIONS\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E\u003C\u002Fa\u003E"}},{"is":"article-image","props":{"type":"inline","caption":"Private Leslie Friston is third from the left in the middle row of this picture. (The Royal British Legion)","imageAlt":"Private Leslie Friston is third from the left in the middle row of this picture. (The Royal British Legion)","url":"https:\u002F\u002Fa57.foxnews.com\u002Fstatic.foxnews.com\u002Ffoxnews.com\u002Fcontent\u002Fuploads\u002F2018\u002F10\u002F640\u002F320\u002FBritishBible3.jpg?ve=1&tl=1","copyright":"","source":"","isSpotlight":false,"responsiveImages":[{"media":"(max-width: 767px)","srcset":"https:\u002F\u002Fa57.foxnews.com\u002Fstatic.foxnews.com\u002Ffoxnews.com\u002Fcontent\u002Fuploads\u002F2018\u002F10\u002F1470\u002F828\u002FBritishBible3.jpg?ve=1&tl=1 2x"},{"media":"(min-width: 767px)","srcset":"https:\u002F\u002Fa57.foxnews.com\u002Fstatic.foxnews.com\u002Ffoxnews.com\u002Fcontent\u002Fuploads\u002F2018\u002F10\u002F1862\u002F1048\u002FBritishBible3.jpg?ve=1&tl=1 2x"}]}},{"is":"paragraph","props":{"text":"Other soldiers&#x2019; Bibles have also been thrust into the spotlight in recent years. In 2016, the Museum of the American Revolution in Philadelphia \u003Ca href=\"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.foxnews.com\u002Fscience\u002Fsoldiers-faith-rare-bible-carried-at-the-battle-of-bunker-hill-has-moving-inscriptions\"\u003Epurchased\u003C\u002Fa\u003E an extremely rare Bible from the Battle of Bunker Hill. The King James Bible, which is on display in the Museum, is inscribed by America